Property details

Spend all four seasons in the POCONOS in this well-maintained mountain CHALET home! Home layout features one bedroom, full bathroom and laundry on the first floor which is super convenient. Second floor offers two spacious bedrooms and a half bath which is perfect for guests. This charming home features living room with wood beams, a free-standing propane stove, hardwood floors, a cozy dining area, and galley-style kitchen complete with all appliances. Additional conveniences include a laundry room with extra shower and a screened-in front porch perfect for relaxing and observing nature. Home boasts of an oversized attached garage with a dedicated work area and could potentially be converted to a game room. Ideal LOCATION...walking distance to MULTIPLE amenities in Bear Creek Lakes such as the pool, south beach, tennis, basketball, bocce ball, horseshoe pits, pickleball courts, clubhouse, walking trails and playground. North beach & boat dock are only a short golf cart ride away. Minutes to Historical downtown of Jim Thorpe, hiking, biking, rafting, skiing and major Pocono attractions. Call today!
